      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially a showroom-quality masterpiece for the truly discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like shine, while the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
